Ipython:
</p>

<p>
<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/IPython/comments/6reiqp/how_can_i_save_and_load_the_state_of_the_kernel/">https://www.reddit.com/r/IPython/comments/6reiqp/how_can_i_save_and_load_the_state_of_the_kernel/</a>
