<p>
How to view the source code of modules and functions you import.
</p>

<div class="highlight"><pre><span></span>source_DF = dill.source.getsource(prova.prova_word)
print (source_DF)
</pre></div>


<p>
Launch python debugger on emacs
</p>

<p>
<code>M-x pdb</code> 
</p>

<p>
Then you enter the script you aim to debug.
</p>

<p>
<code>python3 -m pdb app_local.py</code>.
</p>

<p>
Finally you can enter <code>h</code> in the debugger to display all of the
available options for it.
</p>

